        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "走进办公室的时候，陶正安静地伫立在窗边，眺望着一群远去的飞鸟，陷入自己的思绪里。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "半晌，她回过头，打开终端，调出了一份检查报告。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "看到什么了吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "里芙的神格神经……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "报告表明，里芙体内，目前只存在一套神经系统。难道是她的神格神经消失了？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "看这里。",
        "disable": 0
